<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1338658-does-anyone-know-how-to-pronounce-the">Does anyone know how to pronounce the author&#39;s name?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1338658'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F11507.My_Name_Is_Asher_Lev">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/1338658-does-anyone-know-how-to-pronounce-the">3 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/1338658-does-anyone-know-how-to-pronounce-the">Add your answer</a>
</li>
</ul>
</div>

</div>
<div class='allCommunityAnswers'>
<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/72323450-sarah"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1523308843i/72323450._UY100_CR25,0,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/72323450-sarah">Sarah</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
The c-h of Chaim is pronounced with a guttural Hebrew chet. Chaim is two syllables, like Chai (rhymes with "hi")-im. I believe Potok is pronounced like Puh-tok.
</span>
</div>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerFooter'>

<div class='flagAnswer'>
<a class="right flag" rel="nofollow" id="flag_link722319" title="Flag this answer as inappropriate." href="/flagged/new?resource_id=722319&amp;resource_type=CommunityAnswer&amp;return_url=%2Fquestions%2F1338658-does-anyone-know-how-to-pronounce-the%2Fanswers%2F722319-the-c-h-of-chaim-is">flag</a>
</div>
<ul class='communityQAFooter answerFooter'>
