<li class='cover' id='bookCover_1383176'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/1383176.A_Patch_of_Blue"><img alt="A Patch of Blue" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1387703193l/1383176._SX98_.jpg" />
